data.description: Come enjoy Florida’s Nature Coast living. Located in charming Citrus Springs.  Beautiful 2021 home like NEW. This home features split floor plan, 3 bedrooms 2 bathrooms 2 car garage. Kitchen boast granite counter tops, stainless steel appliance, and planter shelving. Ceiling fans in every room.A screened  Florida room with ceiling fan to enjoy your morning coffee or evening nights to listen to all of Florida's nature without the bugs and great for your family cookouts. NO HOA . Love to golf, hike, bike ride, fish, you will love Cittrus County. Close by to local restaurants and shopping. Near Withlacoochee Trail, Lake Rousseau for it world renowned bass fishing. Gulf of Mexico within 15 driving time. Ocala 45 minutes, Tampa and Orlando 1 hour 45minutes. Citrus County was just voted one of the top 5 places to live in Florida.
